#: ../../../lib/web/src/components/restore-banner.tsx:91
msgid "Your account was moved here from {source}. Until you delete it there, messages and notifications may reach both servers, some of your content keeps being served from the old server, and followers may take a few minutes to find you here."
msgstr "Aistríodh do chuntas anseo ó {source}. Go dtí go scriosann tú é ansin, d'fhéadfadh teachtaireachtaí agus fógraí an dá fhreastalaí a bhaint amach, leanann roinnt de d'ábhar á sheirbheáil ón sean-fhreastalaí, agus d'fhéadfadh sé cúpla nóiméad a thógáil ar do lucht leanúna tú a aimsiú anseo."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:126
msgid "Your account will be permanently deleted on {purgeDate}. You've been signed out. To cancel, sign in again before then."
msgstr "Scriosfar do chuntas go buan ar {purgeDate}. Tá tú sínithe amach. Chun é a chur ar ceal, sínigh isteach arís roimhe sin."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:94
msgid "Your account will be scheduled for deletion and you'll be signed out. You can cancel any time before the deletion date by logging back in. Download your data first if you want to keep a copy."
msgstr "Sceidealófar do chuntas lena scriosadh agus síneofar amach thú. Is féidir leat é a chealú am ar bith roimh dháta an scriosta trí logáil isteach arís. Íoslódáil do chuid sonraí ar dtús más mian leat cóip a choinneáil."

#: src/features/user/replication.tsx:219
msgid "Your account's data on this server will be permanently deleted and you'll be signed out here. Your account stays on your other servers, and you can re-add this one later."
msgstr "Scriosfar sonraí do chuntais ar an bhfreastalaí seo go buan agus síneofar amach anseo thú. Fanann do chuntas ar do fhreastalaithe eile, agus is féidir leat an ceann seo a chur leis arís níos déanaí."

#: src/features/user/data.tsx:180
msgid "Your data"
msgstr "Do shonraí"

#: src/features/user/data.tsx:113
#~ msgid "Your data is downloading"
#~ msgstr "Tá do chuid sonraí á íoslódáil"

#: src/features/user/data.tsx:162
msgid "Your private keys are included, encrypted with this passphrase. Store it safely. You'll need it to restore."
msgstr "Tá do eochracha príobháideacha san áireamh, criptithe leis an abairt phasfhocail seo. Coinnigh í slán. Beidh sí ag teastáil uait chun a chur ar ais."
